{"tid":2133911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"刑事檢控專員請辭 明言與鄭若驊有分歧 提醒同事秉持公正","createTime":"2020-07-31T11:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T12:34:09.000Z","uid":36494,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d973ed629bac7c89eb05deda95665a414f7751e3","tid":2133911,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/PFMHPUKMLWBAAZSAD4F6ZVVXLU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FPFMHPUKMLWBAAZSAD4F6ZVVXLU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG145RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=5dfe42d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FPFMHPUKMLWBAAZSAD4F6ZVVXLU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=fb6160c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/PFMHPUKMLWBAAZSAD4F6ZVVXLU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司高層大地震﹗據了解，刑事檢控專員梁卓然日前請辭，並將於年底離開服務25年的刑事檢控科。梁卓然今向同袍發出電郵透露此事。據悉，梁卓然曾向人透露，與律政司司長鄭若驊在刑事檢控科的運作上出現分歧，久久未能解決，故只能退位讓賢。梁在電郵中提醒律政司同事，要繼續秉持公正和法治精神。"},{"pid":"77227eeb6c57529093fe77f34b938b8797607644","tid":2133911,"uid":55955,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:01:31.000Z","msg":"幾時有公正過？"},{"pid":"fc59e689fa2684b196194e1d5e320c5b79db8eef","tid":2133911,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"41484631563de137d57b909519a91ff926bf9885","tid":2133911,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:01:49.00